[Container]
列出container清單
$ docker container ls

Stop Container
$ docker stop [CONTAINER NAME]

Remove container
$ docker rm [CONTAINER NAME]
Remove all containers
$ docker rm $(docker container ls -aq)

Kill running docker container
$ docker kill [container ID]
kill all containers
$ docker kill $(docker ps -q)

[Image]
Download Image
$ docker run [IMAGE NAME]
$ docker pull [IMAGE NAME]
List Images
$ docker images
Remove Images
$ docker rmi [IMAGE NAME]
Create image
$ docker image build -t ${image_name} path/to/Dockerfile
Remove All Images 
$ docker rmi $(docker images -a -q)

[EXEC]
$ docker exec [CONTAINER NAME] cat /bin/bash

[Docker Compose]
Start Docker
$ docker-compose up 
Stop Container
$ docker-compose stop /


查運行的process
$ docker ps 
查全部的process
$ docker ps -a



